@startuml chat-sequence
!theme plain
title Chat flow: User → API → Yandex LLM

actor User
participant "Frontend\n(mommy-ai)" as FE
participant "Mommy AI API\n(Go/Gin)" as API
participant "Yandex Cloud AI\n/v1/responses" as Yandex

User -> FE: Types message, sends
FE -> FE: Build messages[] (history + new)

FE -> API: POST /api/chat\n{ "messages": [{ role, content }, ...] }
note right of API: CORS allowed

API -> API: Format messages as\n"User: ...\nAssistant: ..."
API -> API: Build request:\n{ prompt: { id }, input }

API -> Yandex: POST /v1/responses\nAuthorization: Api-Key\nOpenAI-Project: folderId\nBody: { prompt, input }

Yandex -> Yandex: Run prompt (e.g. obstetrician agent)\n+ file_search / knowledge

Yandex --> API: 200 { output: [{ content: [{ type: "output_text", text }] }] }
API -> API: Extract output_text from response
API --> FE: 200 { "reply": "..." }

FE -> FE: Render reply as Markdown\n(ReactMarkdown + remark-gfm)
FE --> User: Show assistant message in chat

@enduml
